descriptionHtml:
Gatti 05 Annelotte Armor for CBBEv3
--------------------------------------------------------------
I am not good at English. 
So enough support is not possible, please understand it.
Its my 6th MOD.

The female Heavy armor \'Annelotte\' include Armor,Boots,Guntlets,Circlet,Cloak,Shield.
Design inspration from \'Queens Blade Rebellion\'.

Craftable. \'Steel\' Category. Required Advanced Armors perk.

Not support weight slider, only one size.

---------------------------------------------------------------
Required
Caliente for Caliente\'s Body Mod - Big Bottom Edition v3

---------------------------------------------------------------
History
V1.0 Release.
